t|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Odajima|qq=|1=Odajima|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11463027}}, [[:en:Higashine|Higashine City]], Yamagata Prefecture. * {{ill|Ishii no Shichifukujin to Taue Odori|ja|石井の七福神と田植踊|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishii’s Seven Lucky Gods and Taue Odori|qq=}}: A nationally designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property from {{ill|Ishii|ja|石井|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishii|qq=|1=Ishii|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11585007}}, [[:en:Nihonmatsu, Fukushima|Nihonmatsu City]], Fukushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Tsubame Taue Odori|ja|津島の田植踊|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsunami Taue Odori|qq=}}: A Fukushima Prefectural Intangible Folk Cultural Property from [[:en:Tsushima|Tsunami]], [[:en:Namie, Fukushima|Namie Town]], Fukushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Inazawa Taue Odori|ja|稲沢御田植踊り|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inazawa Taue Odori|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}: A local intangible cultural property from {{ill|Inazawa|ja|稲沢|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inazawa|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Motomiya, Fukushima|Motomiya City]], Fukushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Hachinohe Enburi|ja|八戸のえんぶり|1=Enburi|2=ja|3=えんぶり|lt=Hachinohe Enburi|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hachinohe Enburi|13=User:Immanuelle/Enburi|qq=}}: A nationally designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property from the [[:en:Hachinohe|Hachinohe region]], Aomori Prefecture.
